data.description: Open House Saturday, April 6th from 1-3pm. A detached 24'x28' oversized two car garage with a loft above steals the spotlight of this gorgeous Plattsmouth home! The home features 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, and an attached 1 car garage. Vaulted ceilings welcome you to the open-concept main floor living area. The kitchen makeover boasts freshly painted cabinets, new countertops, butcher block topped island, and SS appliances. Enjoy two separate closets in the primary bedroom with an ensuite full bathroom! In the basement, you'll find two bedrooms and a 3/4 bathroom. The rear deck off the kitchen overlooks the fully fenced backyard. The detached garage comes complete with a 1500lb winch, heat/AC, and 220V service. All main level windows, except kitchen, replaced Dec 2020. Don't miss out on this rare find!
